Beispiel:
```php
$l = [-1, 2, -4, 5, 6];
$positive = getPositive($l);
print_r($positive); // [2, 5, 6]

$l = [5, 3, -5, 2, -3, 3, 9, 0, 123, 1, -10];
$positive = getPositive($l);
print_r($positive); // [5, 3, 2, 3, 9, 123, 1]
```
